graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Admission Controller]
        Controller -->|manages| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod Architecture"
        direction TB
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh<br/>Java Runtime<br/>8033 gRPC, 8080 internal]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>8008 HTTP→gRPC]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Sidecar]
        StoragePuller[Storage Helper<br/>Puller/Init Container<br/>8086 gRPC]
        ModelRuntime[Model Runtime<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe]

        RESTProxy -->|translates to| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes to| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|communicates with| ModelRuntime
        StoragePuller -->|loads models for| ModelRuntime
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR]
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>v1beta1]
        PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>legacy v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/kubectl] -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR
    User -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    User -->|creates| PredictorCR

    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    Controller -->|creates/manages| RuntimeDeployment[Runtime Deployment<br/>ModelMesh + Runtime + Proxy]
    Controller -->|creates| Services[ClusterIP/Headless Services<br/>8033 gRPC, 8008 HTTP]

    RuntimeDeployment -.->|contains| ModelMesh
    RuntimeDeployment -.->|contains| RESTProxy
    RuntimeDeployment -.->|contains| ModelRuntime

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        ETCD[ETCD Cluster<br/>2379 gRPC/HTTP<br/>Model Metadata Storage]
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>443 HTTPS<br/>Model Artifacts]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443 HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
    end

    Controller -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|stores metadata in| ETCD
    StoragePuller -->|downloads from| S3
    Controller -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus
    RuntimeDeployment -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus

    subgraph "Integration Points"
        KServe[KServe<br/>Shared InferenceService CRD]
        ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh<br/>Optional mTLS]
    end

    InferenceServiceCR -.->|schema from| KServe
    Services -.->|optionally uses| ServiceMesh

